<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.7.7">
<l>paritiyo ṭaṇimati paṉivarai ticainilam</l>
<l>eritiyo ṭeṉaviṉa viyalviṉar celaviṉar</l>
<l>curutiyo ṭarumaṟai muṟaicolu maṭiyavar</l>
<l>karutiya kaṇapura maṭikaḷta miṭamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of god who is the means and the motivator for all that is named</l>
<l>The sun, the beautiful moon, snowy mountains, the quarters, land,</l>
<l rend="indent">and blazing fire,</l>
<l>Is Kaṇṇapuram where devotees, who recite the rare Vedas</l>
<l>With [correct] pitch according to rule, meditate.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
